<plot>Sylvester Cat's new hang-out is an inventor's lab, which is near Tweety Bird's house atop a pole. Guarding Tweety's house is a bulldog named Spike. Sylvester invents all kinds of contraptions including a storm cloud, a robot dog, invisible paint, and a retracting grabber. The bulldog foils all Sylvester's attempts to catch Tweety with these inventions.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?621765</url></doc>
